# Architecture Rules

Use Feature First Architecture.

Frontend code belongs in:
frontend/src/features/<feature-name>

Backend code belongs in:
backend/app/modules/<module-name>

Never create at application root:
- controllers/
- services/
- repositories/

Every feature and module must be self-contained.

Cross-feature imports are forbidden.
If two features share logic, extract it to shared/.

Business logic belongs only inside service.py (backend) or hooks/ (frontend).

Prefer modifying existing files over creating new files.

Do not introduce alternative architectural patterns without an ADR in docs/decisions/.
